data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated concrete block home that offers both comfort and versatility. Situated on a spacious lot with NO HOA, this property features a classic ranch design with a modern twist. The heart of the home is the updated kitchen, which boasts sleek butcher-block countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage space. The kitchen island serves as a convenient breakfast bar, perfect for enjoying quick meals or hosting friends and family. One of the highlights of this home is the additional bedroom and a flex room. In addition, the fully-fenced backyard is a true oasis for relaxation and recreation! The home is conveniently located within easy reach of local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Owner has installed a brand new ac. Come view for yourself!
